summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $175.00 out of the General Fund of the City of Seattle, to pay the claim of W. K. Sheldon, Jr., for personal injuries sustained by his wife, Dinah Sheldon, on the 21st day of October, 1913, at 5:30 P.M., at the Southwest corner of North 45th Street and 2nd Avenue Northeast in the City of Seattle, and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
